Tonight at Midnight, the qualifier round to see which 14 Chive Chapters will compete for all the glory of the Chive Cup , will come to a close. To say it’s heated is an understatement and you have to finish hard if you want to qualify to play beer pong for $10,000 to your favorite charity. Finals will be held at Gatsby South, theCHIVE’s Secret Playhouse.
